plans.planDes: Covers damage to your car and others for 1 year

addons.description: Mandatory by law. 15 Lakhs coverage against accidental injury or death.
addons.description_v1: Pays up to {bold} 15 Lakhs{/bold} in case the car owner is permanently disabled or dies in an accident.
addons.description_v2: Stay legally protected with our personal accident cover add-on. In case of accidental injury or death of the car owner, receive up to Rs 15 L.

addons.description: Covers repair or replacement of engine, gearbox, or internal parts, in case of damage.
addons.description_v1: Cover engine and gearbox damage caused by floods or heavy rains, as well as engine damage from oil/coolant leakage during an accident.
addons.display_name_v1: Save yourself from costly engine repairs
addons.display_name_v2: Save yourself from costly engine repairs
addons.description_v2: Extend your coverage to include engine and gear box damages resulting from oil leakage, water entering engine during floods or rains. These damages are not covered in standard plan.
addons.sub_heading: Shield your car engine from rains & floods

addons.description: Get the original invoice value along with registration charges and road tax in case of theft or total loss. Coverage applicable for 1 claim.
addons.description_v1: Get the complete invoice value of your car or the current on-road price, whichever is lower, if your car is stolen or damaged beyond repair.
addons.display_name_v1: Ensure full coverage for total loss
addons.display_name_v2: Ensure full coverage for total loss
addons.description_v2: If your car is stolen or damaged beyond repair, we'll pay you either the complete invoice value (including registration charges and road tax) or the current on-road price, whichever is lower.

addons.description: Protect your loved ones in case of unfortunate accidents. 2 Lakhs coverage per passenger for 1 year against accidental injury or death.
addons.description_v1: Pays up to {bold}2 Lakhs per passenger{/bold} if they are permanently disabled or die in an accident.
addons.description_v2: Protect your loved ones against accidental injury or death. Up to 2 Lakhs coverage per passenger against unfortunate accidents.

primary_description: Covers damages to your car and damages caused to someone elses vehicle or property by your car

primary_description_v1.text: Covers accidental damage to your car
Covers damage caused by your car to others and their property
Unlimited cashless claims at all {bold}{dynamic_make_name} garages{/bold} across India
Free coverage for damage caused by rat bites
Free car pick-up and drop during claims

secondary_description_v1.text: All benefits of the Comprehensive Plan

covered.description: Covers car repairs if your car is damaged in an accident.
Covers car damage caused by fire, self-ignition, explosion or lightning.
Covers car damage caused by natural or man-made calamities such as earthquakes, riots, etc.
Covers the cost of consumables like nuts, bolts, brake oil, engine oil, etc., used during repairs.
Covers car damage caused by rat bites.
Covers damage caused by your car to others and their property.

not_covered.description: Doesnt cover natural wear and tear of parts like tyres, tubes, and engine.
Doesnt cover damage caused to the car if its used for business-related activities (e.g. deliveries, transportation for a fee)
Doesnt cover any car damage that was present before the purchase of this policy.
Doesnt cover any expense arising from traffic law violations like driving without a valid licence or under the influence of alcohol, drugs, etc.

primary_description: Sometimes called Bumper to Bumper plan, includes all the benefits of a standard comprehensive plan while additionally covering depreciation cost of parts

primary_description_v1.text: Covers accidental damage to your car
Covers damage caused by your car to others and their property
Covers full cost of car parts if they are replaced during repairs
Unlimited cashless claims at all {bold}{dynamic_make_name} garages{/bold} across India
Free coverage for damage caused by rat bites
Free car pick-up and drop during claims

secondary_description_v1.text: All benefits of the Zero Depreciation plan

covered.description: Covers the full cost of replaced car parts, saving you from depreciation charges.
Covers car repairs if your car is damaged in an accident.
Covers car damage caused by fire, self-ignition, explosion or lightning.
Covers car damage caused by natural or man-made calamities such as earthquakes, riots, etc.
Covers the cost of consumables like nuts, bolts, brake oil, engine oil, etc., used during repairs.
Covers car damage caused by rat bites.
Covers damage caused by your car to others and their property.

not_covered.description: Doesnt cover natural wear and tear of parts like tyres, tubes, and engine.
Doesnt cover damage caused to the car if its used for business-related activities (e.g. deliveries, transportation for a fee)
Doesnt cover any car damage that was present before the purchase of this policy.
Doesnt cover any expense arising from traffic law violations like driving without a valid licence or under the influence of alcohol, drugs, etc.
